Megan Parkinson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Megan_Parkinson 0 Megan Parkinson is a British actress. She is known for her roles in the TV films Damilola, Our Loved Boy and To Walk Invisible.In 2017, Parkinson appeared in the Season 7 premiere of the HBO series Game of Thrones as Alys Karstark, whose house serves as bannermen to Jon Snow, King in the North. In 2018, Parkinson appeared in the TV series Ackley Bridge as Sam. Megan_Parkinson is a_British_actress .
